The code file AtmSimulator contains common operations performed by ATM machine.
AtmSimulator has a main method to bootstrap the program.
Following options would be provided to user :

1. Deposit
2. Withdraw
3. Display Balance
4. Mini Statement
5. Exit
Select an Option:


